data.description: This 4 bed 2 bath Townhome located in SE Aurora has been updated throughout. This spacious home boasts New flooring, Fresh interior paint, new kitchen cabinets, new granite countertops, all new kitchen appliances, new washer, Dryer 1 years old,  Furnace, Air Conditioner, Hot Water Heater 4 years old. But wait there's more......This home faces south on a large greenbelt, giving you additional privacy and personal space.  Located near major shopping, restaurants, hiking trails, Community Rec Centers, Cherry Creek State Park, several local neighborhood parks, Cherry Creek School District, easy access to public transportation, Light Rail, major highways. Nothing to do here but move-in, unpack and enjoy your lovely new home. This home comes with a 12 month Home Warranty.
